I"ý<p>Suddenly on a green day, the twenty one pilots from three doors down started playing coldplay in our dream theater with love guns and roses in their hands at our beach house beside the porcupine tree.</p>

<p>It was like we realized the evanescence of life. It was like we found our nirvana.</p>

